parameters: "\fs[\v[320]]\fn<\v[319]>I screwed a lot of girls here.\fn<GameFont>\fs[30]"
\n<Dwarf Citizen>Water comes from outside.\.\. Smiths need it,\. but it's also good enough for drinking!
\n<Dwarf Citizen>Once it's gone through the Fortress and keeps going down the Hole,\. though...
\n<Dwarf Citizen>Our Fortress ain't self-sustaining yet,\. but we're working on it.\.\. Soon we'll have farm plots to grow delicious \ii[143] inside!
\n<Dwarf Axeman>The Throne lies ahead.\.\. Go pay your respects ta our Queen.
\n<Dwarf Axeman>Sorry,\. can't talk on duty,\. it's nothing a \fs[\v[320]]\fn<\v[319]>proud dwarf\fn<GameFont>\fs[30] would do!
\n<Dwarf Lookout>One wrong step,\. catgirl,\. and I'll crank it up!
\n<Dwarven Nun>Don't you dare defile my Queen!\.\. Begone!!
\n<\n[1]>So this is why you need your dumb guard even while bathing,\. huh?\.\. Pitiful...
Too many questions for a single catgirl.\.\. There's something weird with her,\. that couldn't be witnessed when they met before.
Maybe this place is far more dangerous than she had expected...
Ruina is indeed taking a nightly bath in the Fortress fountain.\.\.
It's being done silently,\. late at night,\. while the rest of her followers is deeply sleeping after a long day of work...\.\.\. and fight.
\n<\n[1]>Does the legendary "queen" have something to hide?\.\. Why bathing right here?\.\. ...\.\.\.
A green glow comes from inside the pool,\. she's holding onto something,\. while golemfish slowly swim by her feet.
She doesn't blink,\. doesn't even look at her faithful nun,\. watching over her surroundings,\. making sure noone disturbs her leader while she's...\.\.\. like this.
The dwarf seems to be raptured by the light emitted by the gem she's holding and polishing accurately.
\n<\n[1]>That huge gem...\.\.\. that's the one that used to be embedded on her throne's backrest?!\.\. ...\.\.\. Why carrying it all the way here?
It's such an intimate act...\.\.\. maternal,\. even.\.\. She doesn't even notice Neneko standing by the fountain.
\n<\n[1]>So this is why you need your dumb guard even while bathing,\. huh?\.\. Pitiful...
Too many questions for a single catgirl.\.\. There's something weird with her,\. that couldn't be witnessed when they met before.
Maybe this place is far more dangerous than she had expected...
\n<Dwarf Axeman>Queen's room 's in here!\.\. None's allowed in!!
\n<Dwarf Axeman>Th' Queen rarely ever comes ta rest in her room.\.\. She's sharper than me axe!
\n<Dwarven Inkeeper>Oi,\. beastman.\.\. Welcome to "Dwarf Plank Inn".
\n<Dwarven Inkeeper>Need to rest your...\.\.\. tail?\.\. That'll be 25\G.
\n<Dwarven Inkeeper>No \G?\.\. You can go look for a kobold hole outside the Fortress~
